{"tid":1189042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 點樣做底屯門公園啲大媽同廢老？？","createTime":"2019-06-06T15:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T08:06:35.000Z","uid":110271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"547f63fb536b8eeb51f47c68e532b906bcfd23b1","tid":1189042,"uid":110271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"就算之前入境處去拉人 用嘈音去罰錢<br />\n但啲大媽唱一日歌閒閒到都收幾皮嘢<br />\n幾千蚊罰款對啲大媽嚟講根本就好閒<br />\n<br />\n啲廢老又成堆咁圍哂喺到阻撚住哂<br />\n<br />\n拋磚<br />\n羊毛岀自羊身上<br />\n我成日見啲廢老喺到食煙<br />\n每日都搵控煙辦嚟罰啲廢老錢<br />\n咁咪冇錢畀大媽 久而久之去破壞大媽啲生意<br />\n有冇得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21b92e7de3d14f8ebab8531a09a703db53e8ec2","tid":1189042,"uid":110271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"仲可以點做？"},{"pid":"d8d68e6f97307188b0f290ccaa1e6db115437e0a","tid":1189042,"uid":186071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HjDUhO8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjDUhO8.png&h=c1d0d40a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecefbf2902747ce09e395e4c5415936aa9e12676","tid":1189042,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8d68e6f97307188b0f290ccaa1e6db115437e0a","tid":1189042,"uid":186071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HjDUhO8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjDUhO8.png&h=c1d0d40a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f083167ac5235141219ffd42acd3a1ad76215504","tid":1189042,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8d68e6f97307188b0f290ccaa1e6db115437e0a","tid":1189042,"uid":186071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy